WEBVTT

00:00:04.973 --> 00:00:11.131
On your fingertips, you can feel
the centres of other person.

00:00:11.251 --> 00:00:14.673
If something is fishy, you can feel it.

00:00:14.793 --> 00:00:17.837
If somebody's cheating you, can feel it, everything.

00:00:17.917 --> 00:00:21.344
Your fingers speak.
This is what Muhammad Sahib has said:

00:00:21.434 --> 00:00:24.939
"At the time of resurrection, your hands will speak".

00:00:25.047 --> 00:00:27.420
Clearly. How can hands speak?

00:00:27.540 --> 00:00:33.688
This is how. Because all these five fingers
are the centres, sixth and seventh centre.

00:00:33.808 --> 00:00:42.194
One on the physical side, another — on the physical
and also mental side is the right side,

00:00:42.274 --> 00:00:45.542
and the emotional side on the left side.

00:00:45.662 --> 00:00:55.317
These are two different systems within us,
which people are not understanding,

00:00:55.437 --> 00:01:01.102
that there are two channels within us.

00:01:01.222 --> 00:01:05.208
What we call as the autonomous nervous system

00:01:05.328 --> 00:01:08.844
has got the parasympathetic
nervous system in the centre.

00:01:08.964 --> 00:01:12.263
But there are two — left and right
sympathetic nervous systems.

00:01:12.343 --> 00:01:18.383
And these are the systems — two systems —
that are enlightened on your fingertips,

00:01:18.473 --> 00:01:23.659
by which you know exactly what is wrong with you,

00:01:23.749 --> 00:01:27.168
what centres you are catching.
That is self-knowledge.

00:01:27.258 --> 00:01:30.942
People will go mad, but they will not know
they’re getting mad.

00:01:31.062 --> 00:01:34.924
They will have cancer, they will not know
they are having cancer.

00:01:35.861 --> 00:01:42.425
This indication tells you exactly
what’s wrong with you.

00:01:43.163 --> 00:01:50.273
Now, if you know how to correct your centres,
you can correct the centres of others, also.

00:01:50.777 --> 00:01:58.012
Then also, there is another achievement is that
you become collectively conscious.

00:01:58.132 --> 00:02:02.115
Means you can feel others on your fingertips.

00:02:02.223 --> 00:02:05.390
You can feel others on your fingertips.

00:02:05.510 --> 00:02:08.844
Who is the other? That’s what we think.

00:02:08.964 --> 00:02:11.326
But nobody is the other.

00:02:11.434 --> 00:02:18.154
We are part and parcel of one spiritual personality.

00:02:18.244 --> 00:02:23.010
And once somebody has problem,
we immediately know there’s a problem,

00:02:23.118 --> 00:02:25.577
because on the fingertips you can feel it.

00:02:25.685 --> 00:02:30.877
This is true knowledge. Is not some sort of
reading a book or some sort of a thing.

00:02:30.997 --> 00:02:35.571
But is a true knowledge within yourself,
which you know yourself,

00:02:35.651 --> 00:02:38.002
which we call as cognitive science,

00:02:38.110 --> 00:02:40.558
which works within yourself.

00:02:40.678 --> 00:02:44.656
You don’t have to go out to read anything
to understand anything.

00:02:44.776 --> 00:02:51.100
Your own being itself is a
complete computer I should say,

00:02:51.220 --> 00:02:55.225
which tells you what’s what, who is what.

00:02:55.783 --> 00:02:58.908
We have no idea as to what we are.

00:02:59.538 --> 00:03:06.370
We have not been given any idea as to
what potential we have.

00:03:06.490 --> 00:03:10.107
It’s tremendous, it is.
It is tremendous.

00:03:10.215 --> 00:03:15.338
And if it works, it will work for you,

00:03:15.458 --> 00:03:19.014
for your family, for your children,

00:03:19.104 --> 00:03:24.008
for your city, for your nation,
and for the whole world.

00:03:24.128 --> 00:03:29.365
So this has to become
a collective understanding

00:03:29.485 --> 00:03:32.680
within yourself, not mentally.

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:36.571
Mental understanding is just
temporary and passes over.

00:03:36.661 --> 00:03:39.576
But it’s an actualization, again and again I say.

00:03:39.684 --> 00:03:44.342
It’s the actualization of the knowledge
within yourself.

00:03:44.462 --> 00:03:47.740
Then they talk only of that.

00:03:48.442 --> 00:03:54.566
They talk in the words of chakras, of the centres,

00:03:54.686 --> 00:03:59.383
"That person is this", "That person has got this",
"I have got this".

00:03:59.503 --> 00:04:04.470
Now on your fingertips, which gives you
a perfect answer for everything.

00:04:04.590 --> 00:04:08.844
Then it looks after you,
it protects you, it guides you,

00:04:08.964 --> 00:04:13.548
as I told you, and guides you in the right way,
in the right manner.

00:04:13.668 --> 00:04:16.927
And how it achieves things is wonderful.

00:04:17.047 --> 00:04:21.947
So we have to first and foremost understand
that we have to have that

00:04:22.037 --> 00:04:26.662
special personality
of a self-realized personality

00:04:26.782 --> 00:04:30.201
which will really help and care for others.

00:04:30.281 --> 00:04:33.366
It’s not just talking. It’s not just reading.

00:04:33.486 --> 00:04:39.210
It’s not just following some false guru.
But it is following yourself,

00:04:39.330 --> 00:04:43.274
which is to show that you are your own master.

00:04:43.394 --> 00:04:47.789
You become your master,
and you know everything about everything.

00:04:47.909 --> 00:04:50.233
This is the potential in all of you.

00:04:50.323 --> 00:04:54.422
As I said, it is not only for few people.

00:04:54.530 --> 00:04:57.719
It’s not for only black, white people.

00:04:57.839 --> 00:05:03.005
But it’s also meant for people who are uneducated
who are living in the villages,

00:05:03.125 --> 00:05:04.901
who are very simple people.

00:05:04.981 --> 00:05:09.753
It works for all of them.
And when it works you’ll be amazed

00:05:09.843 --> 00:05:13.675
how it transforms you and transforms others.

00:05:13.795 --> 00:05:16.674
And you become so confident about yourself.

00:05:16.794 --> 00:05:22.571
You don’t doubt yourself, because there’s
an absolute knowledge on your fingertips.

00:05:22.691 --> 00:05:26.509
It is something that is within you,
which you should achieve.

00:05:26.629 --> 00:05:32.495
Of course, for this you should know that so far
you have not known, so you have to know.

00:05:32.615 --> 00:05:36.024
As long as you have this attitude it will work out.

00:05:36.144 --> 00:05:41.357
I cannot force. Sahaja Yoga cannot
force on anyone self realization.

00:05:41.437 --> 00:05:43.208
Cannot be forced.

00:05:43.328 --> 00:05:45.233
It has to be asked for.

00:05:45.313 --> 00:05:49.204
Unless and until you knock the door,
it won’t work out.

00:05:49.324 --> 00:05:53.609
It works out for people only
who really want it

00:05:53.729 --> 00:05:58.287
and who want to become self realized.

00:05:58.407 --> 00:06:02.084
As a result, you don’t have any responsibility.

00:06:02.204 --> 00:06:06.570
It’s only the responsibility
of the all-pervading power

00:06:06.690 --> 00:06:08.865
that does everything for you;

00:06:08.964 --> 00:06:14.163
that looks after you, that guides you,

00:06:14.283 --> 00:06:18.426
and takes you to the right places,
to the right situations,

00:06:18.546 --> 00:06:22.853
and guides you in such a manner
that you're amazed.

00:06:22.973 --> 00:06:26.840
How is it? How is it working?
How is it working out?

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:30.707
There will be no meaning left to any miracles.

00:06:30.827 --> 00:06:35.206
But these miracles are not like taking out a diamond,
anything like that.

00:06:35.326 --> 00:06:38.496
But it’s a miracle
how the circumstances will change,

00:06:38.576 --> 00:06:40.389
how people will change,

00:06:40.479 --> 00:06:46.652
how you’ll become such a joyous, lovable personality.

00:06:47.390 --> 00:06:52.173
On this subject I don’t know how many lectures
I have given, and there’s no end to it.

00:06:52.281 --> 00:06:55.273
But I would say that
you should take your realisation

00:06:55.353 --> 00:07:01.413
and go into our programs,
whatever they have,

00:07:01.533 --> 00:07:05.799
and grow into it. Because you take
some time to grow. Like a seed sprouts

00:07:05.919 --> 00:07:08.009
but it takes time to become a tree.

00:07:08.089 --> 00:07:10.186
But hardly one month at the most,

00:07:10.306 --> 00:07:14.323
and don’t have to pay there also.
Again I'll tell you, nothing has to be paid.

00:07:14.403 --> 00:07:18.475
You just give some time to yourself
and it will work out.

00:07:18.595 --> 00:07:23.060
When you have mastered it,
you’ll be amazed what you can do.

00:07:23.180 --> 00:07:25.305
A month at the most.

00:07:26.025 --> 00:07:29.690
Some people just get it and they don’t have to
do anything — just they know.

00:07:29.770 --> 00:07:32.672
But most of the people have to do it.

00:07:32.792 --> 00:07:37.715
It improves everything: your thinking capacity,

00:07:37.796 --> 00:07:41.559
in the sense your brains get enlightened.

00:07:41.679 --> 00:07:44.968
You become a very large-hearted personality.

00:07:45.088 --> 00:07:52.164
And other things that we think of, of prosperity
and all that, all comes through.

00:07:52.284 --> 00:07:58.374
This I’m just telling you, like a mother would like
to give a castor oil with little chocolate on top.

00:07:58.964 --> 00:08:05.029
But main thing is you must know yourself
how great you are.

00:08:05.149 --> 00:08:09.042
That is what every mother wants her child to know.

00:08:09.162 --> 00:08:14.369
That’s my only desire is in America, if it spreads

00:08:14.489 --> 00:08:21.545
in that manner it will all be a great thing,
a great boon for the whole world.

00:08:21.625 --> 00:08:23.247
May God bless you.